This simple script is used to tell whether some new topics appeared in some forum. Filtering on topic keywords is present.
Uses XPath. Can be used with any forum kind. Each instance can use own config.

For Windows install Ruby from RubyInstller and DevTools with installation instructions on same page.

Dependencies:
gem install nokogiri (For Windows in case of x64 ruby and DevTools "gem install nokogiri --prerelease")
gem install parseconfig
gem install unicode_utils
gem ruby-growl

growl - only for Windows notifications

Look for installation instuctions in the INSTALL file.
